          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一日离家一日深，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好似孤雁宿寒林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下张从，乃湖广长沙人氏。奉了双亲之命，上京贸易，看今日天气晴和，赶"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "路要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不分昼夜往前进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "急忙回家奉双亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二强盗同上，同杀张从。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "强盗甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我将包裹分了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二强盗同分包裹，同争一枚金钱。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二路人 （内同白） 嗯哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二强盗",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那旁有人来了！你我将这枚金钱，大家不要，逃走了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二强盗同下。二路人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "我家有棵摇钱树！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得了，你们家哪儿有摇钱树啊，别犯财迷啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你哪里知道，我家有一个果木树，等它结了果，卖了钱，岂不与摇钱树一样！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么说，我也有啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有什么啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听着啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "我家里有个聚宝盆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们家，哪里来的聚宝盆？"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家养活了一个老母猪，等它下了小猪，卖了钱，岂不是聚宝盆么！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别净犯财迷了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！你看那边是个什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老路人看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是一死尸，口内还有一枚金钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们敲出来，咱们俩人分呐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此就敲起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二路人同敲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无量佛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大路旁边一古刹，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "七岁儿童讲道法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "何况庄周是道家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？老丈，你们在此做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们这里敲骨求金呐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，我想世界之上，只有求金葬骨，哪有敲骨求金之理，依贫道相劝，你们"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要敲了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不叫咱敲，跟他要一枚金钱，咱们就不敲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住！他们与我要一枚金钱，方肯不敲，这便如何是好？哦，有了！师"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父教我点石成金之术，待我试来！“天灵灵，地灵灵，石块变成金！”呵，果"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一枚金钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈拿了去，你们不必敲了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老路人接金。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "少路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个老道，是个傻子。咱们还是敲，他要不教敲，咱们跟他要十枚金钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此敲起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老丈，你们怎么又敲起来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老路人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要不教我们敲，得给我们十枚金钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住。看他贪得无厌，我不免谴动神虎，惊散他们。“天灵灵，地灵灵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "神虎速降！”"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形上，二路人同跑下。庄周笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "谴动神虎下山来，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "张牙舞爪把头抬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "少了见了哭悲哀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "放神虎回仙界！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周看虎形，虎形对张从做咬状。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大孽畜，还不归山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见一尸骨倒尘埃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那旁有一死尸，待我掐指算来。此人姓张名从字骷髅，乃湖广长沙人氏，奉了"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双亲之命，上京贸易，被二强人杀死，想我出家之人，焉有见死不救之理，师"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父赐我阴阳宝扇，不免救活与他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "张从生来只爱财！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "谁知一命赴阴台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "救你一命转回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！只因他生前欠下猛虎命债，今神虎衔去喀骨三根，我不免搬动树枝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与他接骨便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "忙将树枝来搬动，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "接骨救命小张从。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "枉教贫道把善行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又无心肝，如何是好？呵！有了！山下来了一只黄犬，我将它杀死，用它心肝"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "救活张从便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（犬形上，庄周打倒犬形。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "将犬打倒地埃尘，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "手持戒刀下无情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为救一命又害一生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！为救一人，害了一犬，背了上天好生之德，如何是好？呵！有了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不免用土作成犬心，救活与它！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "黄土作成了犬的心，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "人心怎比你的心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "阴阳宝扇救活了你！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（犬形下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "摆尾摇头下山林。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周取扇，扇张从。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一扇君子把头抬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "二扇君子眼睁开；"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "活来活去你快活来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！我既将他救活，他醒来，若向我要他的行囊包裹，如何是好？呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有了，我且在此打坐，他有来言，我有去语。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三扇君子四体摆"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "霎时间一阵阵昏迷不醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "三扇君子四体摆"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不见包裹为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "三扇君子四体摆"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才我觉得一阵昏迷，醒来为何行囊包裹，俱已不见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那旁有一道者，想是被他盗去，待我向他要来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃！那一道者，你在此打坐，可曾见我行囊包裹？"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贫道在此打坐，未曾见你行囊包裹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此处四下无人，想是被你偷了去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出家人不爱财，爱财就不出家。想是你打睡之时，行囊包裹被旁人盗去，不要"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诬赖贫道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不还我，我要告你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里去告？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "南华县去告。"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周背躬。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！闻得南华县令，爱民如子，人品非凡，不免借此会他一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周对张从。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君子你饶恕了贫道吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张从",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能饶你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "庄周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是哪里说起！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（庄周、张从同下。）"
        }
      ],
